 <div class="content-sidebar-wrap">
  <main class="content">
    <article class="post type-post format-standard entry">
      <header class="entry-header">
        <h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Find Your Expert</h1>
        <p class="entry-meta"><time>Step 3 of 3: </time>
          <b>What do you need help with?</b>
        </p>
      </header>
      <div class="entry-content" style="padding:0px 20px">

        <div class="alert alert-error">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
          <h4>Error</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="control-group" style="height:100px">
          <label class="control-label" for="tagsInput">What technologies do you want help with?</label>
          <div id="tagsInput" class="controls controls-tags">
              <div id="tagNewForm"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="control-group" style="clear:both">
          <label class="control-label" for="reqBrief">What challenges do you want to solve? <span id="breifCount" class="muted" style="float:right;margin:5px 16px 0 0px">0 chars</span></label>
          <div class="controls controls-brief">
            <textarea id="reqBrief" name="brief" placeholder="We pass your brief onto experts. The more detail you provide, the better help you get.">{{ brief }}</textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="control-group" style="display:none">
          <label class="control-label" for="reqHrs"> Around how many hours of help do you need?</label>
          <select name="hours" class="span2">
            <option value="1">1</option>
            <option value="2" selected="selected">2</option>
            <option value="3-5">3-5</option>
            <option value="5-10">5-10</option>
            <option value="10-20">10-20</option>
          </select>
        </div>

       <div class="control-group pricing-group">
          <label class="control-label">Want to Open source your session recording? </label>
          <div class="pricing rb-group controls">
            <input type="radio" id="pricingOpensource" name="pricing" value="opensource" />
            <label for="pricingOpensource" class="pricingOpensource">Open source <em class="opensource">$<span></span>/hr discount</em> </label>

            <input type="radio" id="pricingPrivate" name="pricing" value="private" checked="checked" />
            <label for="pricingPrivate" class="checked">Keep Private</label>

            <input type="radio" id="pricingNDA" name="pricing" value="nda" />
            <label for="pricingNDA" class="pricingNDA">Organize NDA <em class="nda">+$<span></span>/hr</label></em>
          </div>

        </div>


        <div class="control-group" style="height:86px;margin:12px 0">
          <label class="control-label" for="reqBudget">What's your hourly budget?</label>
          <div class="budget rb-group controls">

            <input type="radio" id="budget1" name="budget" value="80" />
            <label for="budget1">$80</label>

            <input type="radio" id="budget2" name="budget" value="110" checked="checked" />
            <label for="budget2" class="checked">$110</label>

            <input type="radio" id="budget3" name="budget" value="150" />
            <label for="budget3">$150</label>

            <input type="radio" id="budget4" name="budget" value="180" />
            <label for="budget4">$200</label>

            <input type="radio" id="budget5" name="budget" value="270" />
            <label for="budget5">$270</label>

            <p class="budgetExplanation budget1">Access <b>20%</b> of our experts</p>
            <p class="budgetExplanation budget2">Access <b>50%</b> of our experts</p>
            <p class="budgetExplanation budget3">Access <b>75%</b> of our experts</p>
            <p class="budgetExplanation budget4">Access <b>95%</b> of our experts</p>
            <p class="budgetExplanation budget5">Access <b>All</b> of our experts</p>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div class="control-group">
          <label class="control-label" for="availabilityInput">What is your location / timezone, urgency & availability?</label>
          <div class="controls controls-availability">
            <textarea id="availability" name="availability" placeholder="How soon do you need help? What city & timezone are you in?" style="height:70px">{{ availability }}</textarea>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br />
      </div>

      <footer class="entry-footer">
        <div class="form-actions">
          <a href="save" class="save button large">Submit</a>
          <a href="#info" class="back button button-gray large">Back</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </main>
</div>


<aside class="sidebar sidebar-primary widget-area">
  <section class="widget featured-content featuredpost">

 <div class="widget-wrap">
      <h4 class="widget-title widgettitle">Open source, Private or NDA?</h4>

      <article class="entry">
        <span class="alignleft">
          <img src="//2.gravatar.com/avatar/2b22b4cd4f65cbef1331cf07e82e6b27?s=120" class="avatar avatar-65 photo">
        </span>
        <header class="entry-header">
          <h2 class="entry-title">Why Open source your AirPair Session?</h2>
          <p class="entry-meta">
            <span class="entry-author">Prateek Gupta</span>, AirPair Matchmaker
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="entry-content">
          <p>If your code is confidential, leave your session recording as <b>private</b>. We still
          record the session, but only you get access to it, so that you have it as a reference.</p>

          <p>If there is nothing sensitive in your code, we recommend that you choose <b>Open source</b>. On top of getting a $20 per hour discount, we share the knowledge you learn with the community. The recordings are also used to promote our experts.</p>

          <p>If necessary, for an extra fee we can also facilitate your experts to electronically sign an <b>NDA</b> (Non Disclosure Agreement).</p>
        </div>

      </article>

    </div>
  </section>
</aside>

